import { NavLink } from "react-router-dom";

import "./MainNavigation.css";
function MainNavigation() {
  return (
    <nav className="MainNavigation">
      <button className="MainNavigation-home">
        <NavLink className="navlink" to="/home">
          Home
        </NavLink>
      </button>
      <button className="MainNavigation-products">
        <NavLink className="navlink" to="/product">
          Products
        </NavLink>
      </button>
      <button className="MainNavigation-cart">
        <NavLink className="navlink" to="/cart">
          Cart
        </NavLink>
      </button>
      <button className="MainNavigation-bills">
        <NavLink className="navlink" to="/bill">
          Bills
        </NavLink>
      </button>
    </nav>
  );
}
export default MainNavigation;
